PrecisCORPORATION DE CHAUFFAGE URBAIN DE MONTRÉAL (CCUM) INCORPORATION AND SALE AUTHORIZATION ORDER - which authorizes: (a) the Canadian National Railway Company to procure the incorporation of a subsidiary and to subsequently sell 70% of its shares to Compagnie internationale financière et industrielle du Québec CIFIQ Inc. on or before December 31, 1990; and (b) the revocation of Order in Council P.C.1988-2254 of September 29, 1988.
